data.description: ***NEW PRICE!!! PUBLIC OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 1/27/24, 12PM-3PM. Rarely available 3 bedroom, 2 bath townhome at Northpointe Terrace 1 in the highly sought after community of Mililani Mauka. This GROUND FLOOR, CORNER UNIT has a private, enclosed lanai perfect for lounging, BBQing and hosting. Enjoy vinyl flooring throughout this home which backs onto greenery and has a beautiful park and playground just across the street from the complex entrance. Two designated parking stalls, with one right outside your door. Very close to Mililani Mauka Elementary and only minutes away from shopping, dining, and public transportation. Centrally located for favorable commute times and easy access to the H-2 freeway and Schofield & Wheeler military bases. Take advantage of Mililani Town Association's many amenities including recreation centers, pools, playgrounds, tennis courts, basketball courts, skate park and more!! See video : click link/virtual tour icon above.  ***BOOK YOUR SHOWING TODAY!!***
